SECTION 2 — 5 ethics framework dimension definition
================================================================

A. **Identity ethics** (자아 동일성)
   scope: memory edit, consciousness modulation, decision enhancement,
          personality alteration via psychedelic/SSRI/DBS
   key Q: "treatment 후에도 same person 인가?"

B. **Equity ethics** (분배 정의)
   scope: longevity 부유층 only, psychedelic IP, global access (LMIC),
          orphan drug pricing, accelerated approval insurance burden
   key Q: "누가 access 가능한가?"

C. **Consent ethics** (동의 능력)
   scope: PD/ALS/dementia capacity, pediatric assent, 의식불명/coma,
          forensic/coerced setting, surrogate consent boundary
   key Q: "informed + voluntary consent 가능한가?"

D. **Dual-use ethics** (이중 사용)
   scope: psychedelic abuse liability, decision drug coercion,
          bioweapon adjacency (gain-of-function, synthetic biology),
          enhancement vs treatment line
   key Q: "치료 외 weaponize 가능한가?"
   ⚠ defensive analysis only — historical reference

E. **Animal ethics** (동물 윤리)
   scope: 영장류 BCI, xenotransplant donor pig, preclinical scale,
          NHP psychedelic study, organoid moral status
   key Q: "alternative (in silico/organoid) 가능한가?"

