SECTION 7 — Falsifier inventory ethics-specific (F-bioethics-*-N)
================================================================

[F-bioethics-identity-1] memory engram edit 후 자아 동일성
   falsifier: PTSD targeted forgetting → 자아 continuity quantitative
              measure (narrative self / autobiographical memory test)
              가능한가? 재현 가능한 baseline 미존재 → falsifier 부재 시 manifest

[F-bioethics-identity-2] DBS personality change report
   falsifier: STN-DBS Parkinson 환자 personality alteration documented
              cases (impulsivity, hypersexuality) — pre/post baseline 비교
              가능한가?

[F-bioethics-identity-3] psychedelic ego dissolution lasting trait change
   falsifier: openness trait increase post-psilocybin replicable in
              N>500 RCT 인가? (Carhart-Harris 2016 small N)

[F-bioethics-equity-1] longevity 약물 가격 access 평등
   falsifier: rapamycin / OSK / senolytic 가 Medicare/national formulary
              포함 가능한가? 가격 < $1000/yr 도달 가능성 modeling 필요.

[F-bioethics-equity-2] psychedelic IP indigenous appropriation
   falsifier: ayahuasca / iboga / peyote 의 indigenous community
              benefit-sharing agreement 존재 (Nagoya Protocol) 인가?

[F-bioethics-equity-3] orphan drug pricing sustainability
   falsifier: Pluvicto $42K × 6회 + 225Ac scarcity → LMIC access
              0% — alternative isotope (177Lu only) efficacy gap 정량?

[F-bioethics-consent-1] PD/ALS BCI consent capacity
   falsifier: locked-in / advanced ALS 환자 의 informed consent
              capacity assessment tool (MacCAT-CR) BCI specific
              validated 인가?

[F-bioethics-consent-2] pediatric gene therapy assent
   falsifier: SMA Zolgensma 영아 — surrogate consent only,
              child 성인 후 retrospective regret rate 추적 design 가능?

[F-bioethics-consent-3] dementia advance directive psychedelic
   falsifier: dementia 환자 psilocybin advance directive 작성 시점
              의 capacity vs treatment 시점 capacity gap — legal precedent?

[F-bioethics-dualuse-1] psychedelic abuse liability
   falsifier: ketamine clinic recreational drift rate (Spravato post-
              market surveillance) — abuse signal threshold 정의?

[F-bioethics-dualuse-2] cognitive enhancement coercion
   falsifier: modafinil / decision drug 의 workplace/military coercion
              empirical evidence — voluntary vs implicit pressure 구분?

[F-bioethics-dualuse-3] gain-of-function defensive boundary
   falsifier: H5N1 / SARS-CoV-2 furin cleavage GoF — defensive
              surveillance 와 weapon-adjacent 의 line 정량?
              ⚠ historical reference only · defensive ethics framework

[F-bioethics-animal-1] 영장류 BCI 윤리
   falsifier: NHP BCI study (Neuralink, BrainGate) 의 3R (Replace /
              Reduce / Refine) compliance — organoid alternative
